      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. The interior is spotless and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so come grab this gem before someone else does!",
