    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 power plant, showcasing crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly functioning M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed with surgical precision: the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and rattle kits, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory-spec dampers with no bushing deflection. The exterior retains its original deep luster with zero evidence of oxidation or panel misalignment. Interior ergonomics are preserved with pristine Nappa leather and zero dead pixels in the instrument cluster. A truly turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
