      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating applied recently. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the carpets are protected by original factory mats, and the dashboard is entirely free of UV damage or cracking. Every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented service history with every interval performed at the dealership. It sits on a fresh set of performance tires and features a chassis that feels as tight and responsive as the day it was built. For the buyer seeking a collector-grade example that requires zero compromise, this is the definitive choice.",
